Wyrld’s eyes light up looking around the room, that happiness from before pales in comparison to just how ecstatic she is now. You worry if she’ll explode into goo. She focuses herself as Wylatt walks into the room carrying some heavy boxes, despite his bottom heavy build he manages to carry more than you would think a femboy reasonably could and sets them down in the middle of the floor. He gives you both a short nod and heads back into the storage, leaving you and Wyrld to begin unpacking…

